an''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年，欧盟在能源领域的贸易逆差从</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2009</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2402</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元扩大到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2971</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，而制成品领域的贸易顺差从</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1630</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元增加到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1779</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">与</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2009</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年相比，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年欧盟与所有主要贸易伙伴的贸易额均有所上升。欧盟出口同比增幅最快的目标市场依次为巴西、土耳其和中国，而进口同比增幅最快的则为俄罗斯、中国和印度。其中，欧盟对中国出口同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">37%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，从中国进口增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">32%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', ''),
(93, 14, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">据欧盟统计局公布的数据显示，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年欧盟</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">27</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">国货物出口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">13485</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，进口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">14922</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，逆差</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1437</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">32.9%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">其中，贸易顺差位居前列的成员国分别是德国、爱尔兰、荷兰，顺差额分别是</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1524</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">434</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿和</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">423</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元；贸易逆差位居前列的成员国是英国、法国、西班牙，逆差额分别是</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1155</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">641</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿和</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">518</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">中欧贸易增速明显，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年欧盟对华出口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1131</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">37%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">；自华进口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2820</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">32%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', ''),
(94, 14, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 21.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">德国财政部日前表示，德国经济在度过</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年年底及</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年年初的低谷后将继续强劲增长。其在近日公布的财政部月报中分析，就业市场的良好形势将继续支持德国内消费市场。当前对私人收入以及消费的主要影响来自能源价格的上涨，这主要是由于北非部分国家的不稳定因素。但该部门预计德国年均通胀率不会超过</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。德国经济的增长推动力来自出口，国外订单的增长及慕尼黑伊福经济研究所（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">IFO</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）经济专家的乐观预期都表示出口将继续增长。出口的主要动力依旧来自新兴市场国家，同时工业化国家的订单也在增长。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 21.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">德国财政部长在月度报告中称，目前的相关数据表明，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年德国经济将继续保持增长。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年初，制造业增长虽然趋缓，出口增速变慢，但受新兴市场需求推动，出口仍将保持增长的大趋势，就业情况的改善也有利于国内需求的扩大。经济发展的不确定性在于物价上涨和北非的紧张局势，后者成为全球原油供应的不稳定因素。总而言之，德政府对经济发展非常乐观，预期</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年德国经济将增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2.3%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，并希望将赤字减少到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">484</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元以下。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', ''),
(95, 14, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><st1:chsdate w:st="on" year="2011" month="3" day="22" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">3</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">22</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，德国联邦统计局网站发布的数据显示，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年第四季度，德国出口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2563</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">20.7%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。其中，德国对欧盟国家出口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1540</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">18.2%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">；对非欧盟国家出口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1024</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">24.8%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">；对非欧元区欧盟国家出口增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">21.5%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">；对欧元区国家出口增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">16.7%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年第四季度，德国对欧盟区内前三大出口国的出口额分别为：法国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">240</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">+12.2%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）、英国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">153</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">+12.1%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）、荷兰</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">172</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">+29.9%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）；对非欧盟区国家出口量分别为：美国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">176</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">+24.8%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）、中国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">147</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">+39.4%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）、俄罗斯</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">75</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">32.4%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）、印度</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">26</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">+9.6%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）、巴西</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">26</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">20.5%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">同期，德国进口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2170</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">26.7%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', ''),
(96, 14, '<p>2011年1-2月挪威外贸进出口总额为373.68亿美元，比2010年同期增长13.3%。其中出口244.34亿美元，增长9.5%，进口129.34亿美元，增长21.5%。贸易顺差为115亿美元，下降1.5%。2011年1-2月，挪威石油天然气类产品出口总额达148.76亿美元，与去年同期相比增长11%。</p>', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `jk_addonarticle` (`aid`, `typeid`, `body`, `redirecturl`, `templet`, `userip`) VALUES
(97, 14, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><st1:chsdate w:st="on" year="2011" month="3" day="23" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">3</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">23</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，英国政府公布</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">～</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2012</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">财年的预算计划。该预算虽然坚持</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">6</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月提出的财政紧缩计划，但并没有提出新的紧缩开支措施，而是强调这是一个&ldquo;经济增长计划&rdquo;，提出一个新的经济增长模式，即依靠投资、制造业和出口来刺激经济增长。同时，该预算也囊括了一系列缓解民众生活成本压力的措施。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">下调经济增速预期</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">这份预算报告出人意料地大幅下调</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年的经济增速预期，由</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">11</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月公布的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2.1%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">降至</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1.7%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，并将</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2012</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年的经济增速也由原先预测的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2.6%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">下调为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2.5%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">该预算还预测，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年英国的消费物价指数升幅将在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">4%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">至</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">5%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">的高位徘徊，高于之前</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">3%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">的预测，也高出英格兰银行设立的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">的通胀目标。不过该预算也称，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2012</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年这一数字可望降至</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2.5%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">对于联合政府上台以来采取的财政紧缩政策的效果，该预算认为，英国政府的净借款额今后将逐年减少，本年度将降至</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1460</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿英镑（约合</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2365.2</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿美元），</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2012</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年度将进一步降至</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1220</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿英镑（约合</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1976.4</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿美元）。财政赤字占国内生产总值比例也将从目前的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">11%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">左右降至</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2015</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">～</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2016</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年度的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1.5%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">然而，近期不断上涨的大宗商品价格、高企的通货膨胀率以及</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年第四季度英国经济衰退的事实，令英国政府不得不对经济复苏前景的判断趋于谨慎，并决定推出一系列经济改革措施，以刺激经济增长。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">引导商业成为经济复苏引擎</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">英国财政大臣乔治&middot;奥斯本在向议会提交这份预算的演讲中强调，这份预算是一个&ldquo;经济改革计划&rdquo;，改革的重点在商业领域，鼓励本国企业增加活力并希望吸引更多国际资本投资英国，以增加英国商业的活力，使其成为推动英国经济复苏的引擎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">预算指出，英国将加大对公司税的削减力度，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">4</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月将执行的公司税的下调幅度从原先公布的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个百分点增加为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个百分点，此后</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">3</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年内每年再下调</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个百分点。这样一来，到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2014</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年，英国的公司税率将从目前的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">28%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">减至</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">23%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，比美国目前的税率低</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">16</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个百分点，相比法国和德国也分别低</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">11</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个和</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">7</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个百分点。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">同时，英国将为高风险类公司的投资以及中小企业的科研活动提供税收方面的激励机制。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">该预算还宣布，英国将在英格兰建设</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">21</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个企业区，比此前规划增加</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个，以优惠条件吸引企业投资和发展业务，同时放宽向小企业放款的条件。奥斯本希望这一举措能够促进英国经济更加多元化，减少金融业不景气带来的负面影响，并希望借助这一计划复兴制造业，创造就业机会。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">缓解民众生活成本压力</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">为减轻石油价格上涨对普通家庭带来的影响，该预算决定下调燃料税，为此，石油公司将额外支付</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">20</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿英镑（约合</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">32.4</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿美元）的税，以弥补政府财政收入的减少。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">在个人所得税方面，税率将维持不变，但个税起征点在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">4</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月提高</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1000</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">英镑（约合</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1620</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">美元）的基础上，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2012</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年再提高</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">600</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">英镑（约合</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">972</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">美元），这将使几乎所有人不同程度受益。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">该预算还表示，将拨付</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2.5</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿英镑（约合</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">4.05</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿美元）帮助首次购房者购买房屋，预计这项措施将使</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">10000</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个家庭受益。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">不过，这份预算并没有改变奥斯本</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2010</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月提出的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">5</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年内削减</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">800</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿英镑（约合</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1296</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿美元）公共开支的目标。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年伊始，英国已将消费税由</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">17.5%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">提高至</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">20%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。分析人士称这项政策将在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年内为英国政府增加</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">130</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿英镑（约合</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">210.6</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿美元）的收入，并预计未来还会进一步缩减部分社会福利开支。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', ''),
(98, 14, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">据德国联邦统计局公布的最新数据显示，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月，德中双边贸易总额为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">112.75</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">38.65%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。其中，德自华进口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">66.57</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">32.84%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">；对华出口</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">46.18</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元，同比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">47.98%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，德对华贸易逆差</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">20.38</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿欧元。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '', '', ''),
