ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，而</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2009</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年法国经济同比下降</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2.5%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">法国政府预测</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年经济增长率将达</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。法国财长拉嘉德当天在接受美国路透社采访时表示：&ldquo;我将保持这一经济增长率&rdquo;。许多经济学家对法国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年经济增长的预测相对保守，认为将在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1.6%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">～</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1.7%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">之间，欧委会刚刚将其对法国经济增速预期由</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1.6%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">上调制</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">1.7%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">法兰西银行预测</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2011</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年第一季度法国经济将环比增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">0.8%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，将是</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; font-size: 12pt">2009</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年以来最大的季度环比增幅，但接下来的三个季度增速将有所放缓。</span></p>', '', '', ''),
