style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 140%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">同期，中国与菲律宾、新加坡双边贸易增长相对缓慢，增幅分别为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">11.2%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">和</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">14.2%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">。其中对菲律宾出口增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">14.2%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">，进口增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">9%</span><span style="line-height: 140%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">；对新加坡出口增长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 140%; color: black; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0p